  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuizManagerArun
  questions:
  - questionText: 1, Vishnu Sharma narrated the story of two friends. They were ____
    option1: ..a king and his son.
    option2: ...two jackals.
    option3: ...Harry Potter and Hermoine.
    option4: '...a lion and a bull. '
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 724f33fd6c025824a8d5ef6288403723, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 6dc1b93872e7268499ba54acfcbfdc9d, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 8
  - questionText: 2,Why did Vardhamanaka want to go to Mathura?
    option1: To get a job
    option2: To sell his merchandise
    option3: To meet Krishna
    option4: To invest in stocks
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: bc9014e71ca39e94080eec7eb6c65e15, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: dc149c0141806354eaf9a6132404c8d3, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: "3, Who were the two bulls who pulled the cart? \L(Select TWO answers
      that are correct)"
    option1: Vardhamanaka
    option2: Sanjivaka
    option3: Nanadaka
    option4: Amara Shakthi
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c24be19b5c2b76447a37c109e85761cf, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 45edf0bd6276ea940b7d5ffa86e31573, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 4, What happened to Sanjivaka?
    option1: He married  a cow and had  baby calves.
    option2: He stepped on wet soil and got this feet dirty.
    option3: He danced a song with the other bull.
    option4: He stepped on wet soil and was injured.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 442644b571554b84ea2e3c1f5c737a98, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: cbf27a885c957454b8df13538ec17208, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 5, Why did Vradhamanaka leave the forest?
    option1: He was carrying costly merchandise.
    option2: He was scared of tigers.
    option3: He was carrying cheap merchandise.
    option4: He was bored and wanted to continue his journey.
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fe8c8ee96fa45df47bd83a09b16b5556, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: aef3806e97dc24648b86d7d8c5bec194, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 6, How did Sanjivaka grow healthy ? (Select TWO answers that are
      correct)
    option1: He did 100 push-ups every day.
    option2: He stared following and Ayurvedic diet.
    option3: He feasted on the emrald green blades of grass.
    option4: He drank water from River Yamuna.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8f6fe13c4c0eb16418086876f60930ac, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 2c500ec9deb8a0d49a33d4468c33f327, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 7, What was the name of the the lion who lived in that forest?
    option1: Mr. Incredible
    option2: 'Ponniyin Selvan '
    option3: Damanaka
    option4: Pingalaka
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: dfeaa7bc0e7337b458b48912c5e09228, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: f3d85443487e1c64ca7fc4f227211e44, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: "8, When Pingalaka heard Sanjivaka\u2019s roar, why did the lion
      panic?"
    option1: Lions are scared of bulls
    option2: He had never heard any animal roar before.
    option3: He had never heard the sound of a bull before.
    option4: "The roar sounded like a Rakshahasa\u2019s voice."
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6d16e7659c34ce84abb404d824b87f6a, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: ec14c6ddcf6cf5847b38e69d135842e1, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: "9, Who were the two jackals watching all this?\L(Select TWO answers
      that are correct)"
    option1: Karataka
    option2: Damanaka
    option3: Pingalaka
    option4: Sanjivaka
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0f5a68c7fdb32e84eba11b6adfdb31ce, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 98782dda383eedf4ead00bc3f95034ea, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 10, What was Damanaka curious about?
    option1: He was curious to know what flavor of ice-cream his king liked.
    option2: He was curious to know if his mom would allow him to go to a party.
    option3: He was curious to know what had made his king happy.
    option4: He was curious to know what had disturbed their king.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 73b580a64b28c5840834324cb4d9b2fa, type: 3}
